2d4-c76bf52b17ca","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### New Lead Form Submission\n\nServes an n8n-hosted form (Email, Company, Score). Each submission becomes one execution.\n\nNext: Download Source File","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"51030ba9-2e04-d090-c463-694b0798da4d","name":"Note: New Lead Form Submission"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Download Source File\n\nGET ={{ $json.fileUrl }} — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Parse XLSX Contents · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"e5600cb9-3086-1a8e-224c-cc0fcc915dab","name":"Note: Download Source File"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Parse XLSX Contents\n\nParses the incoming XLSX binary into JSON items.\n\nNext: Clean & Reshape Rows","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"330a584f-ac4a-99e4-1586-0ed7869f3eea","name":"Note: Parse XLSX Contents"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Clean & Reshape Rows\n\nCustom JavaScript: Normalize incoming lead records to a stable schema\n\nNext: Rows Pass Validation?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"7e15c963-629f-f2b7-0738-2c9238de92e6","name":"Note: Clean & Reshape Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Rows Pass Validation?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.leadId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Load Rows into Notion · ②→ Quarantine Bad Rows","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"27584c9b-3ae6-afc8-476e-3872bd141166","name":"Note: Rows Pass Validation?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Quarantine Bad Rows\n\nnotion — `insert` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1000],"id":"a8f438e8-897c-d4e1-afbf-54fd5c237ffb","name":"Note: Quarantine Bad Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Rows into Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"223fc1ca-a197-7b83-25ab-926e106595e0","name":"Note: Load Rows into Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"734f6d9a-c9cb-973b-a51c-2dcc38547bf0","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Fingerprint for Idempotency","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"2ce02366-8fb1-f0f5-da9f-0eee5f2b3b85","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per lead (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"7fd46900-93ce-d405-2de1-ccfe8f507383","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"7490f97d-cee6-823b-7041-d4cc0638855d","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"e10a71e9-83af-b1c4-af3e-43e499c69e5c","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Load Previous Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"badd13eb-a2d8-a97c-50ad-c10c91649207","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"70f49336-a395-34df-42a8-1df6c349455d","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"4a9cc2ca-f920-87c6-3b64-8ea970a00933","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"ce1dc844-742d-6b04-6339-e192ca16f5d6","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"ec1d3fe1-054c-a5f2-bd20-b6e7472b924a","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"1c95ab51-ffbd-707e-c37a-037829305982","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty email","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"ff40bcad-9d95-e8ea-15b0-4171006b7fc1","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty email\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"7bf21579-f185-f29e-f761-dfec7c6d70ca","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty email"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"adc15e3f-53d4-3b0e-bf30-7cdf28d112c7","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 100 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"afb228d4-b689-229a-3484-b431f99b68f9","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"85e92694-44bb-dda6-5c4f-605f60ef4f1e","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Notion)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,520],"id":"f4626160-a891-f78a-5d1f-8238fa8ad5ef","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Notion)\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,520],"id":"d0d8cbad-3af0-3bc3-deb2-4b2f275b58be","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Notion)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7770,520],"id":"625544d5-b077-3ce4-5d7b-48cd616f94c1","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Gmail","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,1540],"id":"651adf5b-e56c-2d6f-ebc1-346aa76cab05","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Gmail\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,1540],"id":"2237f443-3f17-0bf1-c293-34c8323d7233","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Gmail"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7770,1540],"id":"4a7dc5b5-a7ad-605c-fe3a-d4a83929a17c","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Log form submissions with MySQL and Gmail on autopilot\n\n**Pattern:** Form Intake · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nLog form submissions with MySQL and Gmail on autopilot. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual enrichment is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Lead Form Submission → Download Source File → Parse XLSX Contents → Clean & Reshape Rows → Rows Pass Validation? → Load Rows into Notion → Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to form intake without manual effort\n- Anyone automating enrichment in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Responds in seconds\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"b141d3e0-d34e-bb0f-b039-08af4aab97b6","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"3f370ffe-590e-a591-66ba-47fe4019d41d","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"92350929-d881-d4aa-eb17-aaceb3c2cf2e","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your enrichment process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"4f47d61e-2f72-7e0a-5087-3c1e1048ad86","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Lead Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Download Source File","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Download Source File":{"main":[[{"node":"Parse XLSX Contents","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Parse XLSX Contents":{"main":[[{"node":"Clean & Reshape Rows","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Clean & Reshape Rows":{"main":[[{"node":"Rows Pass Validation?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Rows Pass Validation?":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Rows into Notion","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Quarantine Bad Rows","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Rows into Notion":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty email":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Notion)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Notion)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Gmail","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Gmail":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Quarantine Bad Rows":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"b253e969-5965-4a35-8199-506e45b8a0bb","id":"FDX04560"}